<!DOCTYPE html>

<html class="dark" lang="es"><head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com?plugins=forms,container-queries"></script>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght@100..700,0..1&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<script id="tailwind-config">
        tailwind.config = {
            darkMode: "class",
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: {
                        "primary": "#ec9213",
                        "background-light": "#f8f7f6",
                        "background-dark": "#1a1612",
                        "neutral-dark": "#2a241e",
                    },
                    fontFamily: {
                        "display": ["Manrope", "sans-serif"]
                    },
                    borderRadius: {"DEFAULT": "0.25rem", "lg": "0.5rem", "xl": "0.75rem", "full": "9999px"},
                },
            },
        }
    </script>
<style>
        .material-symbols-outlined {
            font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 0, 'wght' 400, 'GRAD' 0, 'opsz' 24;
        }
    </style>
<style>
    body {
      min-height: max(884px, 100dvh);
    }
  </style>
  </head>
<body class="bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark font-display text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 antialiased">
<div class="relative flex min-h-screen w-full flex-col overflow-x-hidden">
<!-- Header -->
<header class="sticky top-0 z-50 flex items-center bg-background-light/80 dark:bg-background-dark/80 backdrop-blur-md p-4 justify-between border-b border-primary/10">
<div class="flex size-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary/10">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">menu</span>
</div>
<h2 class="text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 text-lg font-extrabold tracking-tight flex-1 text-center">SKOL BARBERÍA</h2>
<div class="flex w-10 items-center justify-end">
<button class="flex items-center justify-center rounded-full size-10 bg-primary text-background-dark">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[20px]">person</span>
</button>
</div>
</header>
<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="px-4 py-4">
<div class="relative h-80 w-full overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-neutral-dark">
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-background-dark via-background-dark/40 to-transparent z-10"></div>
<img alt="Professional barber at work" class="h-full w-full object-cover" data-alt="Professional barber performing a precision haircut" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCaMkSiOlzuA0E4nH_VCMmOvdg9E6fLQvw7DcuFrAzEi_GGFBMRmdanjxJaH01agKg1y70rirnh2a7_flsZG5thxT_U6PGwUw2YozPe-Jvcowa3H3s-lUeM2DJB-1T4h3YH-VEQ9Rxdy0zogxlJ3m32wS4Pw3A906a04jit5FVn9kacSR4t1osgbLAqeLQpJJDi2kYAvdC2KreEzhO-n9rXBw4t2wO76gTU1C82QxpWc-wIkfslZKMvUVA6OWR57cGOkoY5Ok-SEh1K"/>
<div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 p-6 z-20 w-full">
<span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 mb-3 rounded-full bg-primary text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-background-dark">Premium Experience</span>
<h1 class="text-white text-3xl font-extrabold leading-tight tracking-tight">Estilo y Tradición</h1>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Introduction -->
<section class="px-6 py-4 text-center">
<p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-base leading-relaxed">
                Descubre la combinación perfecta entre técnica clásica y modernidad en un ambiente diseñado para el hombre actual que valora la excelencia.
            </p>
<div class="mt-6">
<button class="w-full py-4 bg-primary text-background-dark font-bold rounded-xl shadow-lg shadow-primary/20 hover:scale-[1.02] active:scale-[0.98] transition-all">
                    Reservar Cita Ahora
                </button>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Services Section -->
<section class="px-6 py-8">
<div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-6">
<h3 class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight">Servicios Core</h3>
<a class="text-primary text-sm font-semibold" href="#">Ver todos</a>
</div>
<div class="space-y-4">
<!-- Service Item 1 -->
<div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-neutral-dark border border-slate-200 dark:border-primary/10">
<div class="flex size-12 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary/10 text-primary">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">content_cut</span>
</div>
<div class="flex-1">
<h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">Corte de Cabello</h4>
<p class="text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Asesoría de imagen y lavado premium.</p>
</div>
<div class="text-primary font-bold">$25</div>
</div>
<!-- Service Item 2 -->
<div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-neutral-dark border border-slate-200 dark:border-primary/10">
<div class="flex size-12 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary/10 text-primary">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">face</span>
</div>
<div class="flex-1">
<h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">Afeitado Clásico</h4>
<p class="text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Toalla caliente y navaja tradicional.</p>
</div>
<div class="text-primary font-bold">$20</div>
</div>
<!-- Service Item 3 -->
<div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-neutral-dark border border-slate-200 dark:border-primary/10">
<div class="flex size-12 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary/10 text-primary">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">brush</span>
</div>
<div class="flex-1">
<h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">Cuidado de Barba</h4>
<p class="text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Perfilado y nutrición con aceites.</p>
</div>
<div class="text-primary font-bold">$15</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Location Preview (Minimal) -->
<section class="px-6 py-4 mb-24">
<div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-primary/5 border border-primary/20">
<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">location_on</span>
<span class="font-bold">Visítanos</span>
</div>
<p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Av. Principal 123, Distrito Central.</p>
<div class="mt-4 h-32 w-full rounded-lg overflow-hidden bg-neutral-dark relative">
<img alt="Map location" class="h-full w-full object-cover opacity-50 grayscale" data-alt="Map showing barber shop location" data-location="Madrid" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBeyz_xh7avrxnvavbmttJNYZe_RN2y6SAnAbYDkeWbkNJsosRRh0i8nLZkMbCVIxlmJrM9gFtiKBRa9Pcgc_YneQO9CkVxkHsxJhq6a66vOERZVAQD_dLiHVbzxJQ-M2PirLySAMI-MeYmhCnjN2y2l5bE2WTycoLiOTuM3gPvka7YTC95CGe7qVPWD4o2L-2C5djZqow-g3Umj84LZpFyafv8tP2bk73JCRoRG0XTnkD4J93gvy2W79ghq76a-cwq3aaQ5ZaNRR-H"/>
<div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
<div class="size-8 bg-primary rounded-full animate-pulse border-4 border-background-dark"></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Bottom Navigation Bar -->
<nav class="fixed bottom-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 flex border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-primary/20 bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark/95 backdrop-blur-lg px-4 pb-6 pt-3">
<a class="flex flex-1 flex-col items-center justify-center gap-1 text-primary" href="#">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined fill-1">home</span>
<p class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Inicio</p>
</a>
<a class="flex flex-1 flex-col items-center justify-center gap-1 text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500" href="#">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">content_cut</span>
<p class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Servicios</p>
</a>
<a class="flex flex-1 flex-col items-center justify-center gap-1 text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500" href="#">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">calendar_month</span>
<p class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Citas</p>
</a>
<a class="flex flex-1 flex-col items-center justify-center gap-1 text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500" href="#">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">account_circle</span>
<p class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Perfil</p>
</a>
</nav>
</div>
</body></html>
